{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":86706,"duration_api_ms":59898,"num_turns":12,"result":"The tests pass and the fix is clean. Here's the summary:\n\n**Root cause:** The DSL parser stores config values like `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")` with the `file(...)` wrapper intact. The `handleAPIStepContent` handler was using this raw value directly as a file path (e.g., trying to read a file literally named `file(\".cloche/prompts/implement.md\")`), which always failed.\n\n**Fix:** Added `unwrapFileRef()` helper that strips the `file(\"...\")` wrapper to extract the actual path, applied to both `prompt` and `script` config lookups in the handler.\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"f859d082-0f5e-4b4e-b172-aed8cb5e717f","total_cost_usd":0.43761900000000004,"usage":{"input_tokens":13,"cache_creation_input_tokens":28848,"cache_read_input_tokens":385308,"output_tokens":2584,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":28848,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":13,"outputTokens":2584,"cacheReadInputTokens":385308,"cacheCreationInputTokens":28848,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.43761900000000004,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"aaf6cadd-53b7-417c-abfd-91d1cad3e82b"}
